WEBVTT

00:02.068 --> 00:05.455
Cheers is filmed before
a live studio audience.

00:06.373 --> 00:07.874
Sammy, got three questions.

00:07.874 --> 00:10.377
One, who's going to fix the ball return

00:10.377 --> 00:11.244
on the pool table?

00:11.244 --> 00:13.463
Okay, I'll check that today.

00:13.463 --> 00:15.665
Check. Two, how much vermouth
do you want next month?

00:15.665 --> 00:17.467
Uh, an extra case.

00:17.467 --> 00:19.219
Check. Three, why, why, why?!

00:19.219 --> 00:20.470
Oh, come on, don't start with me

00:20.470 --> 00:21.971
about the wedding, will you?

00:21.971 --> 00:23.473
Oh, Sammy-- Sam,
it actually looks

00:23.473 --> 00:25.842
like you're going to go through
with this horrible thing.

00:25.842 --> 00:28.812
Why do you want to marry this woman?

00:31.147 --> 00:33.483
I don't know, Carla. It...

00:35.485 --> 00:38.238
It's not easy to explain.

00:38.238 --> 00:40.023
I mean, why did you marry Nick?

00:40.023 --> 00:42.409
Why?! 'Cause I was stupid, that's why.

00:43.660 --> 00:45.328
Well...

00:45.328 --> 00:47.280
actually, there was a little more.

00:49.282 --> 00:50.283
What?

00:50.283 --> 00:52.285
You tell anybody this,
and I'll kill you.

00:52.285 --> 00:53.787
(muttering): No, I won't.

00:53.787 --> 00:55.288
(sighing)

00:55.288 --> 01:00.794
Nick made me feel... all...

01:00.794 --> 01:03.680
(sighing): all squooshy inside.

01:03.680 --> 01:06.516
"Squooshy"?

01:06.516 --> 01:08.384
Squooshy.

01:09.803 --> 01:11.805
Uh, well...

01:12.305 --> 01:13.807
that's how Diane
makes me feel--

01:13.807 --> 01:14.808
all squooshy.

01:14.808 --> 01:16.309
(yelling): Oh, yuck!

01:16.309 --> 01:17.193
Double yuck!

01:17.694 --> 01:18.695
Oh, I'm gonna throw up!

01:18.695 --> 01:20.063
This is so disgusting!

01:20.063 --> 01:21.364
You said it. What do y...?

01:21.364 --> 01:23.366
I married Nick 'cause he knocked me up.

01:23.366 --> 01:24.617
This is sickening!

01:24.617 --> 01:25.401
Ugh!

01:25.401 --> 01:27.403
I only said it 'cause you said it.

01:27.403 --> 01:28.905
What are you do...? I need some air.

01:28.905 --> 01:30.406
Hey, guys, listen to this!

01:30.406 --> 01:31.407
No, don't, please don't...!

01:31.407 --> 01:33.409
Sam says Diane makes
him feel all squooshy!

01:33.409 --> 01:34.911
(crowd taunting)

01:34.911 --> 01:36.162
MAN: Ooh, Sammy!

01:37.464 --> 01:38.965
"Squooshy."

01:38.965 --> 01:40.967
Oh!

01:41.968 --> 01:45.972
(piano plays)

01:45.972 --> 01:47.974
? Sometimes you want to go ?

01:47.974 --> 01:53.480
? Where everybody knows your name ?

01:53.480 --> 01:57.984
? And they're always glad you came ?

01:57.984 --> 02:00.487
? You want to be where you can see ?

02:00.487 --> 02:03.490
? Our troubles are all the same ?

02:03.490 --> 02:07.994
? You want to go where
everybody knows your name. ?

